        -:  392:/** Applies the visitor \a visitor to the whole coefficients of the matrix or vector.
        -:  393:  *
        -:  394:  * The template parameter \a Visitor is the type of the visitor and provides the following interface:
        -:  395:  * \code
        -:  396:  * struct MyVisitor {
        -:  397:  *   // called for the first coefficient
        -:  398:  *   void init(const Scalar& value, Index i, Index j);
